title: Giuliani Invents New Level Of Shamelessness, Elon’s NeuraStink 1.26.22

description:
In episode 1071, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Zahra Noorbakhsh to discuss Quick thought: Biden calling Doocy stupid SOB legitimized his presidency?, Giuliani’s Cavalcade of Cash Grabs Continues With Autographed 9/11 T-Shirts, Elon Musk’s Neuralink is Even Stupider Than You Think and more!

  1. Laura Ingraham's Attempt at Comedy
  2. Giuliani’s Cavalcade of Cash Grabs Continues With Autographed 9/11 T-Shirts
  3. Butt Lovin' Unicorn
  4. Collectible Autographed By Rudy Giuliani 9/11 20th Anniversary T-Shirt
  5. Rudy Giuliani’s Legal Fund Was a Bust. Now, Its Donation Page Has Disappeared.
  6. Elon Musk’s Neuralink is Even Stupider Than You Think
  7. Elon Musk’s Neuralink is hiring a clinical trial director
  8. A quick guide to Elon Musk’s new brain-implant company, Neuralink
  9. ELON MUSK UNVEILS WORKING NEURALINK CHIP THAT CONNECTS BRAIN DIRECTLY TO COMPUTER
  10. Scientists used a tiny brain implant to help a blind teacher see letters again
  11. ELON MUSK’S NEURALINK IS "BAD SCIENCE FICTION," BRAIN SCIENCE PIONEER SAYS


LISTEN: Thousand Finger Man by Candido

Follow: @ZahraComedy
